name: Croocy #88
description: At someplace, there is much crocodiles who are relaxing and waiting for prey to come to cross the river. Not long after that, it wasn't prey but heavy equipment and human workers who wanted to make the river to become the new capital city. The crocodiles who saw it, immediately swam to the river, till’ they didn't realize they were at the bottom of the river and passed through the dimensional portal under the river. But, Their life completely different now, this crocodiles group like entering the animal dimension with other habits. All the animals there, have different clothes and characters. The crocodiles feel that in this new place they will get a better life, and this is the daily life of the crocodiles in the new place. So, this is a new life about Croocy, a group of crocodiles on the other dimension.
